Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.05,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so that you won't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k28}fu{\k28}wa{\k20}ri{\k0} {\k24}ko{\k50}ko{\k28}ro{\k0} {\k21}ma{\k50}i{\k23}a{\k28}ga{\k25}re{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.85,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Soar up to the sky with your gentle heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\k17}{\k28}a{\k21}no{\k0} {\k45}ka{\k38}ze{\k0} {\k20}ni{\k0} {\k26}no{\k46}se{\k95}te{\k0} {\k13}i{\k5}s{\k27}se{\k7}i{\k0} {\k10}e{\k26}ro{\k372}se{\k0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:26.84,OpTranslation,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ride on that wind, and get it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:53.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come by to see the fireflies?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:01:59.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it was almost the season for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:04.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:09.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you were a bit too early, time and season-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Their numbers have dropped too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:26.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:33.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she possessed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see me even though you're a human child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:57.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a careless human child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:08.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bothering with me, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you possessing that person from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can see Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:24.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:27.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to talk a lot to him when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:30.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, we were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:35.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he suddenly couldn't see me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't see you anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can that even happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:47.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When people become adults, those kinds of powers tend to become weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So that happens too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:56.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he would be getting married soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I would at least see his big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:06.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our relationship was a lot like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:13.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship is that of a master and pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Try guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:25.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Blonde hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! It's pond woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:31.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a low-level Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I didn't have a name in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a name, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Curly-noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be able to talk to another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in your care until the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, what do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about Curly-noodles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:57.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about Curly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dull radiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to sleep already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:21.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, I had a dream where someone was calling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:33.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:43.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:46.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:02.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, I have to go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:06.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How about "Kiyo?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How about "Kiyo" as your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming unable to see Youkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So that can happen too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:31.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, there was a mountain god in this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,that fell in love with a human woman, and they would rendezvous secretly at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:42.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,During those times, the fireflies from this pond would light the way for them in the pitch-black darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:50.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,To thank them, the mountain god turned the short-lived fireflies into Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:56.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In their joy, many of them left the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:02.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and the fireflies here are said to be the descendants of those who stayed behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just a legend, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:30.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:38.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,the one from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:44.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, I think I tripped over something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a feisty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something in this pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure. Besides the fireflies, I guess there are carp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ayakashi doesn't attack people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't ask him if he could see Youkai too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to see a human who could see them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:35.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and asking them about their past would just be trouble for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:40.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:45.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is called Akifumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he could see Ayakashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:53.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,he suffered much from the looks he got from his family and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He would come here to cry by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and I would hide quietly and watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:04.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, he came during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In a rush, I tried to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:09.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but something caught onto my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:22.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:24.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we talk for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested in humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:38.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in Youkai, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He came the next day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked and talked so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, we would play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how it feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:07.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:19.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But on one day, his eyes could no longer see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't notice even if I touched him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He would come to the pond and I would call for him several times,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,yet he couldn't see me even when I stood right in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'll be unable to see us one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:54.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if you'll be unable to see us one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:57.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:05.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that my wish for the longest time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:12.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I had always, always wished to be free from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:55.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He can no longer see Kiyo's fleeting light,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so why does he continue to go to the pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:04.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you can see Ayakashi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:10.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A Youkai I met recently told me you could once see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about it, it was all like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:24.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was tough on me because I was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:29.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to get along well with one Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:30.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:32.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:42.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, I suddenly couldn't see Ayakashi at all anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:50.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't forget about her, so I didn't get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:51.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:56.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But I finally met a girl I could love with all my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's a very nice person, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Our wedding ceremony will be held in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't come here anymore, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Akifumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:31.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He found someone important to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:39.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:52.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,On that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a peaceful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:59.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably Kiyo's memory that flowed into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see you! Please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:39.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,...love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:57.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:04.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:29.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,not Akifumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you were called, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw and heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a firefly Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to keep it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm able to return to being a simple bug just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:55.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you won't be able to keep your current form,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and your life will end as a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:11.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He will continue to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at the very least,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:20.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,even as a bug,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's not intending to head towards the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:38.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That huge, big-mouthed guy doesn't attack humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:40.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but he eats fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's going around and eating them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:46.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,all the fireflies here are hiding somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Hotaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:57.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:59.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:24.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:32.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Hotaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell... it's someone else's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:50.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom got really mad then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:13.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:20:01.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did everything go well for the mountain god and his lover that the fireflies protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:06.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Ayakashi, humans have a short lifespan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:09.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:13.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the day come when I can't see them either?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:18.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,These one-sided encounters and these troubling days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:23.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be liberating for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:37.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that the small firefly whispered something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:42.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't understand the bug's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Hotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he understood them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe only he could...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:15.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough when you can't do anything, even though you can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any obligation to help out everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Youkai and humans are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you this, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:34.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you couldn't see us anymore, I wouldn't let you get away until you give me the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:40.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Youkai before me disappear one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:45.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,the memories from my encounters with them will never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you make an effort to be my bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:55.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised, right, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:21:59.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And they will never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single one.
